OL,7,FConsumer confidence in the future of
OL,8,Fthe UK economy has plummeted to its
OL,9,Flowest level since the height of the
OL,10,Fcost-of-living crisis, according to a
OL,11,Fsurvey.
OL,13,FAlmost two-thirds of consumers (64%)
OL,14,Fbelieve the economy will get worse
OL,15,Fbefore it gets better, according to
OL,16,Fthe Which? Consumer Insight Tracker.
