OL,5,Cshock'
OL,7,FConfidence in future household
OL,8,Ffinances also fell significantly, by
OL,9,F10 points to minus 19 ` the lowest
OL,10,Flevel reported since July 2023 ` while
OL,11,Fconfidence in current household
OL,12,Ffinances dropped six points to minus
OL,13,F21.
OL,15,FThis comes as the estimated number of
OL,16,Fhouseholds missing essential payments
OL,17,Fsuch as rent or mortgage, utility
OL,18,Fbills, credit card or loans remained
OL,19,Fat similar levels to March, at 1.9
OL,20,Fmillion households.
